body:
**Warning! This mod is only in alpha, however its survival ready.**

Simple Raider Guns is a Minecraft mod that adds the guns and items from a really popular computer game called Arc Raiders.
Craft guns, fight Arc and immerse yourself in the dangerous world of Arc Raiders.

[ALSO AVAILABLE ON CURSEFORGE](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/simple-raider-guns)

**For NOW the mod adds:**

![Pre update crafting table.](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5815ec320fa45cec3cb520b8f408b020acc74fce.png)

-A workbench;

-Light ammo;

-Stitcher;

-Hairpin;

-Kettle;

-Rattler;

-Medium Ammo;

-And more;

**Planned features:**

-Shield;

-All the rare,epic and legendary guns.

-All the crafting components;

-New workbenches;

-Some small arc(Wasp,Hornet,etc..)
